{"id": "pos021", "name": "Audio_Xmas_701_12_24", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma...... Aroma？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... Eh? Sister?\nSorry, I fell asleep...\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "It's alright. If you're tired, feel free to rest some more.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Tuner-san]"], "content": "<i>Notice: 10 minutes until performance~ 10 minutes until performance~</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Ah, looks like you're taking the stage soon.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Got it. I'll be ready in a minute.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Ah, it's so cute. Everyone is waiting in Christmas clothes.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Because it's a Christmas event. Aroma, your outfit today is very cute as well.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Christmas...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "What's wrong?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Nothing. It's just... I think I just had a dream about a time when we were both little...?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Eh? For real!? What did you dream about?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Hmm... I'm not very certain, but it seems like sister was working part-time at a piano bar.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Oh, so it's \"Heaven Note\". Is it a shop with a stage for performances?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Yes. Now I remember. I think it's Christmas that day as well. I was still a little girl and I visited the shop to see you... I even sang on-stage later that day.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Yes! This is great news! You remember another thing from your childhood! I have to tell Noah.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "That song... I think it's...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "《 Winter Games》, right?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Yes. I think I still remember how to sing that song.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... Can I sing this song when I take the stage later? I can't really recall the emotion I was in when I sang it back then. If I sing it again, perhaps I will remember that feeling as well.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Of course you can! Alright, time's up. Say hello to everybody~\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Okay.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma……Aroma？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……ん……あれ？お姉ちゃん？\nごめん、寝ちゃったみたい……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "大丈夫よ。疲れたなら休んでなさい。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[チューナー君]"], "content": "<i>本番マデあと10分デス\n本番マデあと10分デス</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あら、もうそろそろ準備しないと。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん、分かった。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "わ、可愛い。\nみんなクリスマスの服着てる。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "だって今日はクリスマスイベントだもの。\nAromaの今日の衣装も可愛いわよ。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "クリスマス……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "どうしたの？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "なんでもない。\nただ、さっき小さい頃の夢を見たの。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "え？本当に！？何の夢！？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うーん……あんまり覚えてないんだけど、お姉ちゃんがピアノバーでバイトしてた。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あぁ、「Heaven Note」ね。\nステージのあるお店でしょう？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "そう、思い出した。\nクリスマスでね、私はまだ子供で、お姉ちゃんに会いにお店まで行ったの……それで、ステージで歌った。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "そうよ！\nまた子供の時のことを一つ思い出したのね！\nNoahに教えてあげなきゃ。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "あの曲……確か……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "《 Winter Games》でしょ？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん、そう。\nたぶんまだ覚えてる。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……今日の舞台で、歌ってもいい？\nあの時どんな気持ちだったか思い出せなくて、でも、歌えば何か思い出すかも。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "もちろんよ！\n時間よ。\nみんなに挨拶してらっしゃい。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん、\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma……Aroma？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……咦？姊姊？\n抱歉，我睡著了……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "沒關係，累了就多休息吧。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>提醒：距離表演時間還有十分鐘～距離表演時間還有十分鐘～</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊，馬上就要上台囉。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "好的，我準備一下。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "啊，好可愛喔，大家都穿著聖誕服在等。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "因為是聖誕節活動嘛，Aroma 今天的造型也很可愛喔。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "聖誕節……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "怎麼了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "沒事，只是剛剛好像夢到我們小時候的事情……？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "咦？真的嗎！？夢到些什麼？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……不是很清楚了，不過姊姊好像在一間鋼琴酒吧打工。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊，「Heaven Note」啊，是不是有一個表演舞台那個地方？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "對，我想起來了，好像也是聖誕節那天，我還很小，跑去店裡找妳……後來還上台唱歌了。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "對呀！太好了，又想起一件小時候的事了！得跟 Noah 說才行。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "那首歌……我記得是……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "《 Winter Games》對吧？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯，我好像還記得怎麼唱。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……等等上台可以唱這首嗎？我想不太起來當時是什麼心情，如果能唱的話也許會想起來。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "當然可以！好了，時間到了，去跟大家打招呼吧～\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma……Aroma？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……응? 언니?\n내가 잠들었나 보네...미안해.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "괜찮아. 피곤할 텐데 푹 쉬도록 해.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[튜너군]"], "content": "<i>공연 시간까지 10분 남았습니다~\n공연 시간까지 10분 남았습니다~</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "아, 바로 또 무대에 서야 하는구나.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "응. 가서 준비할게.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "와, 진짜 귀엽다. \n모두들 산타 복장을 하고 기다리고 있어.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "크리스마스 이벤트니깐. Aroma, 오늘 네 의상도 꽤 귀여운걸?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "크리스마스……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "왜 그러니?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "아무것도 아니야. 방금 전 잠깐 잠들었을 때 우리 어렸을 때 꿈을 꾼 것 같아서.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "응? 정말이야!? 무슨 꿈이었어!?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "음……가물가물한데...언니가 피아노가 있는 레스토랑에서 아르바이트를 하고 있었던 것 같아.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "아~ 「Heaven Note」말이구나. \n무대가 있었던 그 레스토랑 말이지?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "응! 지금 생각났어. 그때도 아마 크리스마스였던 것 같은데...내가 아주 어렸을 때, 언니를 찾으러 그곳에 갔었어...그리고 그 무대에 올라가서 노래도 불렀었고...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "맞아! 드디어 어렸을 때 기억을 또 하나 생각해냈구나! 정말 잘 됐어! Noah 한테도 알려줘야겠다!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "그때 불렀던 곡이……내 기억엔……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "《 Winter Games》, 맞지?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "응. 맞아. \n아직 어떻게 불러야 하는지 기억하고 있어.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……조금 이따 무대에서 그 노래 불러도 돼? 그때 내가 어떤 심정으로 그 노랠 불렀는지 아직 기억이 나지 않아. 만약 노래를 부르다 보면 생각날 수도 있을 것 같아.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "물론이지! \n좋아, 시간 다 됐어. 자, 이제 무대로 가자.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "응.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma……Aroma？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……咦？姊姊？\n抱歉，我睡著了……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "沒關係，累了就多休息吧。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>提醒：距離表演時間還有十分鐘～距離表演時間還有十分鐘～</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊，馬上就要上台囉。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "好的，我準備一下。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "啊，好可愛喔，大家都穿著聖誕服在等。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "因為是聖誕節活動嘛，Aroma 今天的造型也很可愛喔。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "聖誕節……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "怎麼了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "沒事，只是剛剛好像夢到我們小時候的事情……？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "咦？真的嗎！？夢到些什麼？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……不是很清楚了，不過姊姊好像在一間鋼琴酒吧打工。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊，「Heaven Note」啊，是不是有一個表演舞台那個地方？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "對，我想起來了，好像也是聖誕節那天，我還很小，跑去店裡找妳……後來還上台唱歌了。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "對呀！太好了，又想起一件小時候的事了！得跟 Noah 說才行。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "那首歌……我記得是……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "《 Winter Games》對吧？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯，我好像還記得怎麼唱。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……等等上台可以唱這首嗎？我想不太起來當時是什麼心情，如果能唱的話也許會想起來。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "當然可以！好了，時間到了，去跟大家打招呼吧～\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma……Aroma？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……咦？姊姊？\n抱歉，我睡着了……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "没关系，累了就多休息吧。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>提醒：距离表演时间还有十分钟～距离表演时间还有十分钟～</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊，马上就要上台啰。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "好的，我准备一下。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "啊，好可爱喔，大家都穿着圣诞服在等。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "因为是圣诞节活动嘛，Aroma 今天的造型也很可爱喔。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "圣诞节……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "怎么了吗？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "没事，只是刚刚好像梦到我们小时候的事情……？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "咦？真的吗！ ？梦到些什么？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……不是很清楚了，不过姊姊好像在一间钢琴酒吧打工。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊，「Heaven Note」啊，是不是有一个表演舞台那个地方？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "对，我想起来了，好像也是圣诞节那天，我还很小，跑去店里找妳……后来还上台唱歌了。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "对呀！太好了，又想起一件小时候的事了！得跟 Noah 说才行。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "那首歌……我记得是……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "《 Winter Games》对吧？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯，我好像还记得怎么唱。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……等等上台可以唱这首吗？我想不太起来当时是什么心情，如果能唱的话也许会想起来。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "当然可以！好了，时间到了，去跟大家打招呼吧～\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}